Interface ResponseListener


  • public interface ResponseListener
    This interface should be implemented in the Server to receive processed instruction responses.

    • Method Detail

      • onInstruction

        default boolean onInstruction(Instruction instruction)
                       throws NjamsMessageFormatException
        This calls the correct onInstruction(...Response) method if the command in the instruction has a corresponding Response class.
        Parameters:
        instruction - the incoming instruction
        Returns:
        true, if a corresponding response class was found and used, else false
        Throws:
        NjamsMessageFormatException - could be thrown while processing one of the onInstruction methods
